            <paragraph>After starting the server (<reference internal="True" refid="class-udpserver-method-listen"><inline classes="std std-ref">listen()</inline></reference>), you will need to <reference internal="True" refid="class-udpserver-method-poll"><inline classes="std std-ref">poll()</inline></reference> it at regular intervals (e.g. inside <reference internal="True" refuri="class_node#class-node-private-method-process"><inline classes="std std-ref">Node._process()</inline></reference>) for it to process new packets, delivering them to the appropriate <reference internal="True" refuri="class_packetpeerudp#class-packetpeerudp"><inline classes="std std-ref">PacketPeerUDP</inline></reference>, and taking new connections.</paragraph>
